title: SpaceSwap generative NFT collection voting proposal
body:
The SpaceSwap platform is planning to release a new generative NFT collection that will be created specifically for the project. 

The advantages of this collection for the SpaceSwap community are:

Additional products that draw attention to the project
New use cases for MILK2 and SHAKE (part of the collections will be available for purchase using MILK2 tokens with subsequent burning; we plan to use MILK2 for breeding; MILK2 and SHAKE will be used as game currency)
Interactive component - individual elements of the lore will be subject to a DAO vote

There will be more features appearing as the project develops, leading to more use cases for our native tokens.

Please cast your vote on the concept of the collection.

Option 1

Comic-based concept featuring sci-fi, romantic comedy and action, where the main character travels through time and space, visiting various locations that are inhabited by anthropomorphic animals (we’ll start with a COW for sure). Space Amazon cows, bull market battle trader bases, sacred cows versus dog meme coins and more. Unlimited space for building individual mini-games and the ability to create special NFT characters with history and personality.

Option 2

A much loved food and drink concept - shaken, not stirred, with a cherry on top. The purchase of ingredients and the production of food, which can then be implemented in a virtual cafe and incorporated into a larger economic game concept.

Option 3

In case you don’t like any of the two above — please, pick this variant and suggest your own idea. Let us know via Twitter, Telegram or Discord, adding the hashtag #SpaceSwapNFT.
